<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Reset - Gentric</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }

        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .reset-message {
            background-color: #fff3e0;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #ff9800;
        }

        .reset-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #f44336;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .reset-button:hover {
            background-color: #d32f2f;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .security-note {
            background-color: #ffebee;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border-left: 4px solid #f44336;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">Gentric</div>
            <p>Password Reset Request</p>
        </div>

        <div class="reset-message">
            <h2>Hello, {{firstName}}!</h2>
            <p>We received a request to reset your password for your Gentric account. If you made this request, click
                the button below to reset your password.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="{{resetLink}}" class="reset-button">Reset Password</a>
        </div>

        <div class="security-note">
            <h4>ðŸ”’ Security Notice:</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>This password reset link will expire in 1 hour</li>
                <li>If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email</li>
                <li>Your password will remain unchanged until you create a new one</li>
                <li>For security reasons, do not share this reset link</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <p>If the button above doesn't work, you can copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
        <p style="word-break: break-all; color: #666;">{{resetLink}}</p>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Â© {{year}} Gentric. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>